{"tid":2362709,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(G)I-DLE 舒華的中國粉絲站中斷專輯代購","createTime":"2021-01-11T15:38:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T15:43:11.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6938ae8b47148ebf2804341dc554bd7f1ef496c8","tid":2362709,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T15:38:19.000Z","msg":"(G)I-DLE - 火花 part分配 (theqoo)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://theqoo.net/square/1799338451\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheqoo.net%2Fsquare%2F1799338451&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2Ba%2FFu68%2BWP7gD6%2BC1gzqbK8%3D&h=fcb4849e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theqoo.net/square/1799338451</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kaAEubr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkaAEubr.jpg&h=0ade67b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舒華彷彿是&quot;生火吧&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(G)I-DLE 舒華的中國粉絲站中斷專輯代購<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://theqoo.net/square/1799526557\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheqoo.net%2Fsquare%2F1799526557&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2Ba%2FFu68%2BWP7gD6%2BC1gzqbK8%3D&h=8fe33e95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theqoo.net/square/1799526557</a><br />\n<br />\n【公告】<br />\n<br />\n  大家好，這裡是ShuHua_葉舒華中文首站。<br />\n  很抱歉舒首選擇在今天告訴大家一件事，這件事情是舒首剛剛做出的決定，希望能夠<br />\n得到大家的支持。<br />\n  自從舒首開站以來一直都很支持cube的各項工作，每一次專輯代購都沒缺席，甚至在<br />\n站內人手不夠充足的情況下依然進行了本次回歸的代購。並且為了鼓勵大家對於此次專輯<br />\n的購買，舒首站內也做出了相應的活動。但是讓我們非常痛心的是，今日下午北京時間5<br />\n點公開的新歌《HWAA》中，成員舒華僅有3.9秒的個人part，並且MV鏡頭只佔有17秒。這<br />\n件事情讓我們感到非常困惑。<br />\n  我們認為作為公司，cube應該合理規劃旗下所有藝人的發展。但是根據各方面情況顯<br />\n示，公司並沒有真正重視舒華，反而自omg回歸以來，舒華個人part不斷減少，對於舒華<br />\n的個人妝造不夠上心。這件事令眾多舒華的中國粉絲感到很寒心。<br />\n  舒首決定順應多數舒華中國粉絲的要求，即日起停止所有專輯代購事宜，專注於舒華<br />\n個人應援，直到葉舒華的職業生涯得到更合理的規劃，並獲得更適合她的個人part。<br />\n  <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tULfGtF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtULfGtF.jpg&h=ceb2b4d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3785dd907a07989474d2da17bc6fd9ffef8a678c","tid":2362709,"uid":215249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T15:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中國台灣粉絲"},{"pid":"019aa5e67b0dfe35c2a3ff3fb966fdb26449fe4d","tid":2362709,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T15:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z748v3N.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz748v3N.gif&h=2b44c90c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}